snippet.textDisplay: I had goosebumps all over my body, I am an Indian born in 94. I remember how underrated this song was, yet it was played constantly on 9xm. I am huge fan of Pakistani singers. I can't believe this song was sung by a Pakistani artist back then, I just came to know❤. Clearly remember the last line of this song...'Vo kehte hai na.' Sadly we 90s kids are too nostalgic about that kind of music and those days now.
